              <div class="swiper-slide"><img src="https://ik.imagekit.io/greenraven/MJ/Testimonials/Testo%20(7)%20(1)%20(1).png?tr=w-700,h-1244,cm-pad_resize,bg-FFFFFF,q-85,f-webp" alt="Community win" width="700" height="1244" loading="lazy" /></div>
